description: Open a new account with us anytime, anywhere with digibank using these easy steps.
Close your DBS/POSB Deposit Account via digibank Online.
Updating of personal particulars have never been simpler. No more queueing up at the branch to update your personal details
Apply for a ATM Card via digibank
Replace or block your ATM card(s) immediately using our online services and request for a replacement instantly.
Apply for a Debit Card via digibank
Replace or block your Debit card(s) immediately using our online services and request for a replacement instantly.
You can activate your new Debit card easily using digibank
You can activate your new ATM card easily using digibank
With our enhanced digibank mobile, you can now update your ATM Cards, Withdrawal limit instantly! (Applicable only for active cards)
With our enhanced digibank mobile, you can now update your Debit Card's NETS, Withdrawal and 3rd Party Funds Transfer limit instantly! (Applicable only for active cards)
Register and activate your digibank now and experience a simpler way of banking anytime, anywhere.
You can now easily retrieve your statements via digibank.
With Digital Token, you no longer need to wait for SMS OTPs or depend on your physical token to authenticate your banking transactions.
Change your address with us easily via digibank
Keep your email address updated to receive your transaction alerts, so you are notified of your account activities.
Update your Personal Details, Signature Records or Passport Number (for foreigners) if you have recently changed it.
Keep your mobile number updated and ensure your transaction alerts on digibank app and mobile device are turned on, so you are notified of your account activities.
Transfer funds easily to another DBS/POSB account via digibank or our DBS/POSB ATM.
digibank allows you to perform Overseas Funds Transfer to over 200+ markets in more than 30+ currencies anywhere, anytime.
Enable your Card for overseas usage to transact and withdraw foreign currency overseas.
